        <Parent_String>Venetian lace [300264609], needle lace [300231662], lace (needlework) [300132861], needlework (visual works) [300264072], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
